      "soil_description": "Rocky, calcareous, well-drained limestone soils, including clays, loams, and sands. Usually in calcareous rocky soils and clays.",
      "drought_tolerance": "High",
      "native_distribution": "Southern Oklahoma south through north-central, central, and west Texas, west to New Mexico, and south to Puebla",
